description:
Data from Cunningham project (https://homes.cerias.purdue.edu/~ssw/cun/) reformatted to JSON format.
Table 2LM: Aurifeuillean factorization of 2^(4k+2)+1=L*M where L = 2^(2k+1)-2^(k+1)+1 and M = 2^(2k+1)+2^(k+1)+1.
Only m = 4k+2 where a full factorization of both M and L are known are included.
Data are taken from April 6, 2022 file at https://homes.cerias.purdue.edu/~ssw/cun/pmain422.txt
Reformatted to JSON by Chai Wah Wu, June 3, 2022.
